Hacker News newest stories ids

Source: R/api.R
get_new_stories_ids.Rd

Retrieves newest stories ids using Hacker News API

Usage

get_new_stories_ids()

Value

list of new stories ids

Examples

# \donttest{
# get ids of new stories on Hacker News
new_stories_ids <- get_new_stories_ids()
new_stories_ids
